<h2 style="font-family:verdana; color:#333">100 Beads Abacus</h2>

<div style="line-height:2">
<p style="font-family:verdana; color:#333">The 100 Beads Abacus contains 10 rows of bead, and each row contains 10 beads. The two coloured beads enable children to subitize quantity easier.</p>

<p style="font-family:verdana; color:#333">Click on the beads, they will automatically slide to the left to show a number. For example, when 3 rows of beads add 5 more beads will make 35. The children able to visualize 35 have 3 tens and 5 ones. This digital tool can also be used to count in 1, 2, 5 and 10. To make the number box hidden or visible, click<img src="https://alfaandfriends.com/maths-digitaltools/00-icons/ui_visibility.png" width="40" height="40" style="vertical-align:middle">.</p>
</div>